---
title: Roast Vegetable Bianca Pizza with Cheddar & Rocket
description: Pizza bianca or "white pizza" in Italian, refers to pizza with no tomato sauce. Sometimes topped with a combination of cheeses and a few simple ingredients, we think it's one of the best pizzas you'll ever try. You'll never even miss the tomato sauce!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/easy-roast-vegetable-bianca-pizza-718a238f.jpg
